Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可急着去救戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:03:00.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让我们在这里浪费时间啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散魂铁爪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱上戈薇的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这女人不是食物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁敢偷吃 我就宰了他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.37,0:03:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖狼族的钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的双腿与右手上都有四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:46.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用速度把犬夜叉耍得团团转的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.45,0:03:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖狼族正与极乐鸟一族战斗着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那似乎是为了夺取极乐鸟手上的四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.02,0:03:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为我能看见四魂碎片所以被劫持了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这样下去 我和七宝都有可能会被吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有七宝也好 我希望他能逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…七宝？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 叫你站起来听到没有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 钢牙 你要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.09,0:04:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把这女人带出去放一下风
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里都是野兽的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害 演技太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.93,0:04:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 银太 白角
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们去保护钢牙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银太他们早就出去巡逻了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:47.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟钢牙一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么？那刚才那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:08.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个…竟敢骗本大爷！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:05.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是死路啊 戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝 你能变成泡泡飞起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是不知道能不能载得动戈薇啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.22,0:05:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会让你们跑掉啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝 去把犬夜叉他们叫来 快！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶的丫头 看我不吃掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.51,0:05:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:02.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 不是跟你们说不准偷吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.55,0:06:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.95,0:06:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个小家伙已经跑得那么远了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们去追他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙 你就饶了我们好不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想被杀掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦…你是为了让同伴逃走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.71,0:06:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就当我的女人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢…钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女人用完以后不是要吃掉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.48,0:06:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那女人不是人类嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这女人能看见四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不只有极乐鸟有碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能收集到这附近所有的碎片哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能得到所有的碎片吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们可就天下无敌了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.73,0:06:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.50,0:06:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙比普通的妖怪女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要有用得多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:07:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫做戈薇对不对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.01,0:07:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天开始你就是我的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.58,0:07:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 不要碰我啦 笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙打了钢牙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那女人要被杀了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.83,0:07:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然叫人家做你的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样太没礼貌了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经有男朋友了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会是那只臭狗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 就是那只臭狗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 是犬夜叉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我男朋友可是有着犬夜叉这个好听的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准你叫他臭狗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你跟他有一腿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在胡说什么啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉喜欢的明明是桔梗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.63,0:07:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样正好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来就打算再见到那家伙非宰了他不可的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要那个叫犬夜叉的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个世上消失的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:13.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该就没有问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 它们是妖狼族的同伙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 弥勒 你也来帮帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就让这些妖怪抓走好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.28,0:08:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢？法师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这一带是这些妖怪的猎场的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该散落着许多狼的骨骸才对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:56.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这里却根本没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:09:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那它们果然与妖狼族联合了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.70,0:09:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的怀疑是很合理的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:03.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我被他们抓走的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.70,0:09:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以找到他们的巢穴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可以救出戈薇他们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事都解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.35,0:09:21.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要被抓走的那个就算不是我是你也行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.59,0:09:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.62,0:09:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的身体不是比我的更结实嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法师 不是要追吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先保持一段距离观察一下再说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒 我要跟你交换！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:43.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得快点找到犬夜叉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉也被抓走了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才离开了一下就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:58.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我不够灵光…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:10:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25}笨蛋 笨蛋 笨蛋 我这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 七宝 你没事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.82,0:10:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.89,0:10:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒 珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.26,0:10:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看 犬夜叉被抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.76,0:10:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战术？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:08.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜那些妖怪会带我们到妖狼族的巢穴去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.40,0:10:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖狼族跟极乐鸟是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇现在是在妖狼族的巢穴里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.27,0:10:20.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里真是狼的骸骨之山啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.15,0:10:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们跟极乐鸟是敌人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 听到没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.28,0:10:31.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在最讨厌的不是妖狼族和这些怪鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我放开
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在最想干掉的就是弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒 跟我决胜负！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他这样说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我们快去救戈薇小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒你给我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把我丢在这里啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弟兄们 都准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.81,0:11:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座山就是极乐鸟的巢穴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:21.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这座山的某处藏着拥有四魂碎片的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.39,0:11:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要找出那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.07,0:11:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.44,0:11:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 四魂之玉碎片一定就在这山中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须得到那四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 快点来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被它们发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杂碎就交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉到四魂碎片的气息了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一边战斗一边找太难了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看见四魂碎片了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.69,0:12:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 妖狼族的小鬼 我们等你好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.53,0:12:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身体中有四魂碎片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:12:58.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们兄弟俩一直想要得到它
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你居然自己送上门来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.07,0:13:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们的想法都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 四魂碎片在什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:11.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碎片就在他们的嘴里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要四魂碎片的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我们吃掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.23,0:13:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.07,0:13:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护好戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.37,0:13:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…可是你想干什么？钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把这个刺进那家伙的嘴里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这个去夺取它们嘴里的四魂碎片？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:43.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一个人太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.85,0:13:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能跟那傻大个交手的只有我了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 大嫂 我们去安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.46,0:13:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大嫂？你在叫我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.59,0:13:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是你啰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:13:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你是我们少主的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 怎么连你们都乱说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往你们那边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.33,0:14:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大嫂 危险
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大嫂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点救他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.61,0:14:15.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会被抓回巢穴里吃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大嫂…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.75,0:14:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.62,0:14:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射中了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.26,0:14:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:37.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这女人怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.27,0:14:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.16,0:15:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚 弥勒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:15.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.04,0:15:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖狼族跟极乐鸟正在进行决战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之要先想办法解决掉极乐鸟才行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.68,0:15:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了 让我来收拾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想死的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:32.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都给我退下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.47,0:15:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么招术啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:52.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭狗 正麻烦的时候你却跑来捣乱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在没空陪你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就饶你一命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:15:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快滚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:15:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你抓走戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要在这里跟你算总账
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 臭狗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:09.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以饶你一命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过不准你碰我的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.86,0:16:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“我的女人”？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.23,0:16:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她能看到四魂碎片的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在是太适合当我的女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:18.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你说什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇小姐 他这么说哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是的啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是那家伙自作多情罢了而已呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那家伙…竟敢胡说八道！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇是我的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱上戈薇了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.48,0:16:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇跟我在一起才幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起跟弱小的臭狗在一起要好得多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不让戈薇有丝毫留恋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早晚会把你也干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后啊 戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也就会毫无保留地爱上我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是霸道的家伙啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 应该是惹人羡慕的性格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.01,0:17:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开口闭口都是戈薇戈薇戈薇的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:09.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别叫得这么亲密啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 不是跟你说现在很忙的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回去快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.43,0:17:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙君 那个家伙在更上面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙…君？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.81,0:17:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要再上吗 已经快到顶了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.19,0:17:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我的这一招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼头你还送上自己的右手了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手臂上的碎片被抢走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.03,0:18:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.54,0:18:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的目标是我双腿的碎片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.45,0:18:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你…你又想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我闭嘴好好看着 瘦狼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.86,0:18:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你见识一下我有多强
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:19:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有两个四魂碎片了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大哥 力量…力量涌出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引出铁碎牙真正威力的轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.24,0:19:16.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风之伤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.04,0:19:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.74,0:19:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把那只大怪鸟一击就干掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经掌握了风之伤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:52.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然碍事的大怪鸟解决掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:58.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轮到我们两人一决高下了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然抱在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还说要决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是那种时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙受伤了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.16,0:20:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点小伤…算不了什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙 你撑着点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…为什么要袒护那小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.60,0:20:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这种货色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:20.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只用左手也能把你干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还敢神气啊 接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.31,0:20:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 给我坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在赶快逃吧 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.02,0:20:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钢牙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.16,0:20:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们闪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.20,0:20:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么故意放他们走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.83,0:20:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…他受了这么重的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.57,0:20:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他们本性也还不坏…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.37,0:20:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还说他不坏？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.88,0:20:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.91,0:20:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你不是被劫持还差点丧命吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.08,0:21:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话…话虽如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.98,0:21:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他也还是保护了我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然动情了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:08.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉 被人家这么华丽地告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.59,0:21:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫戈薇怎么恨他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可笑了 我不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是极乐鸟身上的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和钢牙被极乐鸟抢走的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小子还会回来抢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.58,0:21:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉下次再遇到钢牙的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.58,0:21:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是又非得拚个你死我活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.78,0:21:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去安慰一下犬夜叉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.89,0:21:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他先前真的很担心你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.93,0:21:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这么下去他还真有点可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.90,0:21:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.80,0:21:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 让你替我担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.70,0:21:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你及时赶来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.67,0:22:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实别来救你比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.41,0:22:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那家伙的花言巧语捧得心花怒放
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.31,0:22:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花言巧语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.11,0:22:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说钢牙喜欢我的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.32,0:22:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很在意吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.62,0:22:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在意什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.05,0:22:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我根本没放在心上！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.76,0:22:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就很在意嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.66,0:22:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先说清楚 我对钢牙一点意思都没有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.16,0:22:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁…谁也没问你那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.03,0:22:25.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.83,0:22:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.24,0:22:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上你跟他发生了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.91,0:22:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底在怀疑我什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.28,0:22:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你刚才一直那样看我的啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.35,0:22:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你要冲着我发脾气啊！？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.36,0:22:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪你有那种奇怪的误会啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.79,0:22:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.03,0:22:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不想看到你这张脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.19,0:22:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便你去哪好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.86,0:22:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.17,0:22:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珊瑚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.30,0:23:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.77,0:23:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云母借我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.07,0:23:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.27,0:23:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会是去找钢牙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.38,0:23:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回自己家！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.01,0:23:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
