Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.19,0:23:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才…才不可怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.69,0:23:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不怕呢！可恶！
